      <title>static</title>
      <link href="/2021/12/28/java%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0/java_static/"/>
      <url>/2021/12/28/java%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0/java_static/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://gitee.com/jyxzwd/blogpic/raw/master/img/51ea33290796430a1cae451a6ef37f92.png"></p><p>/**</p><ul><li><strong>成员变量</strong>：</li><li>1，静态成员变量，<u>用static修饰，</u>（属于类，在内存只加载一次，其实表征的</li><li><em>是类中相较于实例成员变量来说，更具有一般化，即共有化的属性，相当于是归并中的归并）</em></li><li>如实时在线人数</li><li>一般使用类名.静态成员变量访问(A101)</li><li>2，实例成员变量（存在于每个对象当中）</li><li>它表征的是对象所共有，但，但是，但是更为个性化的属性（如在线人中各个人的id，年龄等）</li><li>一般使用：对象.实例成员变</li></ul><hr><ul><li><strong>成员方法</strong>（访问方式同成 员变量）</li><li>1，静态成员方法</li></ul><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">public <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">static_app</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    public <span class="keyword">static</span> int num;</span><br><span class="line">    private <span class="built_in">String</span> name;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    public <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">void</span>  <span class="function"><span class="title">getmax</span>(<span class="params">int a,int b</span>)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(a&gt;b?a:b);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    public <span class="keyword">void</span> learn (<span class="built_in">String</span> name)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(name+<span class="string">&quot;niu&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    public <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="function"><span class="title">main</span>(<span class="params"><span class="built_in">String</span>[] args</span>)</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        num--;</span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(num);<span class="comment">//(A101)</span></span><br><span class="line">        static_app t1 = <span class="keyword">new</span> static_app();</span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(t1.name);<span class="comment">//A(102)</span></span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">        static_app.getmax(<span class="number">3</span>,<span class="number">5</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        t1.learn(<span class="string">&quot;cjj&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
